Do we have a comprehensive list of all the consoles that use the DE9 mostly-digital gameport?<br /><br />I know the 2600 uses this (and I think the C64 uses the same?)<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">X → ← ↓ ↑<br /> Y G 5 1<br /></div> where X and Y are potentiometers to &quot;5&quot; and capacitors to either &quot;5&quot; or &quot;G&quot; (&quot;AC ground&quot;)<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3512">lidnariq</a> — Sat Oct 07, 2017 2:55 pm</p><hr />
